rows.field_316025: I'm Kendra! I love to knit and go hiking in my free time. I work as an event coordinator. I have two dogs that love peanut butter.
My name is Camila. I love sunny beach days and beach volleyball. I work as a recruiter for the company.
I go by Jimmy. I love trying new food, and I handle all the human resources related issues.
The name is Pareetha. I love biryani and visiting different temples. I'm amazed by architecture.
I love to play basketball and eat burgers. I go camping about 7 times a year, and I grill almost every other weekend. There's nothing like the great outdoors.
I love trivia. Museums are cool to visit in my spare time.
I enjoy drawing and painting. Listening to piano is one of my favorite past times. I love going to live shows and watching performances. I'm located in Buffalo, NY.
I love talking to my family and spending time with them. We always have such a good laugh.
The name is Chloe. I like watching the latest movies and catching up on sleep in my free time.
My name is Parvathi. When I'm not working, you'll usually catch me chasing after my 3 children.
I go by Rence, and I'm fascinating by true crime documentaries as well as historical documentaries. Fascinating stuff!
My name is Cosmas, and funnily enough, I love all things Cosmos. I am fascinated by astronomy and what lies beyond this planet. I'm based out of Chicago.
I'm Loraine. I enjoy meditating and going on runs. I'm trying to run in the Boston Marathon! Send any running tips my way.
